<h2>Key points </h2><ul><li>Watch for symptoms from the time the injections are done until four weeks after the injections.</li><li>Your child can resume all of their regular activities when they feel able to do so.</li><li>If your child has any difficulty breathing, severe weakness and/or an allergic reaction, take them to the nearest Emergency Department right away.</li></ul>
</div>
